title: OnePlus 10 Pro shows up early at online retailer that hints price will be roughly the same
content:
It’s been over three months since the OnePlus 10 Pro was announced in Europe, and now we finally know when the device is coming to the rest of the world. A retailer in Germany is hinting that the price of the OnePlus 10 Pro won’t change all that much.

more…

The post OnePlus 10 Pro shows up early at online retailer that hints price will be roughly the same appeared first on 9to5Google.
description: According to an early online listing, the price of the OnePlus 10 Pro will be roughly the same as its predecessor.
